I need to know which upcoming reminder you want moved, so I can pinpoint the correct one. Right now all I can tell the system is “some reminder in the future.”  
Here are a few easy ways you can help me identify it:

- Tell me the exact text/title (or even a distinctive phrase) of the reminder.  
- Tell me the original date and time it’s scheduled for.  
- Tell me anything unique you remember—like a place you added to it or the day it was created.

With any one of those pieces of information I can use the search tool to find the exact reminder, then move it to tomorrow at 5:00 PM.
